{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium testimonial carousel section for a Shopify homepage.
    
    The section should feature:
    
    A centered headline and short subheading at the top
    
    A horizontally scrolling carousel of customer testimonials
    
    Each testimonial card includes:
    
    Customer lifestyle image or video
    
    Short quote (1–2 lines max)
    
    Customer name
    
    Linked product name
    
    Carousel behavior:
    
    Auto-scrolls smoothly from right to left
    
    Infinite loop
    
    Pauses on hover (desktop)
    
    Swipeable on mobile
    
    Shows 3–4 cards on desktop, 1 card on mobile
    
    Design style:
    
    Minimal, luxury aesthetic
    
    White or soft neutral background
    
    Clean typography using body font
    
    No heavy borders
    
    Soft shadows or none
    
    Ensure the section is fully responsive, fast-loading, and accessible., I need video volume control option, Need border radius option and Aspect ratio control option too, i Want 14 testimonials and don't wrap the quote, I want to show the complete quote
    
    Also I want the carousel can be controlled with cursor(on desktop) and touch(on Mobile)
    
    I want to turn on and off the terstimonial slide, I need the video link to be accepted from shopify media
{% enddoc %}
